From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 19:21:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(starry/fs): ext4/bind mounts and umount2 busy handling

- sys_mount: MS_BIND via BindDirFilesystem; ext4 on spare /dev/vd* disks;
  reject unknown fstypes and 9p with ENODEV; ENOTBLK for non-vd sources.
- sys_umount2: EBUSY when files are open unless MNT_DETACH or MNT_FORCE.
- QEMU toml comments document optional second disk + 9p args for selfhost.

Made-with: Cursor

